OL,3,CIncrease in pregnant women losing
OL,4,Ctheir job, study suggests
OL,6,FUp to 74,000 women lose their job
OL,7,Fevery year for getting pregnant or
OL,8,Ftaking maternity leave, new research
OL,9,Fsuggests.
OL,11,FThe figure has increased from 54,000 a
OL,12,Fdecade ago, according to campaign
OL,13,Fgroups Pregnant Then Screwed and Women
OL,14,FIn Data.
OL,16,FTheir survey of 35,800 parents found
OL,17,Fthat 12% of women are sacked,
OL,18,Fconstructively dismissed or made
OL,19,Fredundant whilst pregnant, on
OL,20,Fmaternity leave or within a year of
OL,21,Freturning from maternity leave.
