OL,6,FThe report estimated that this could
OL,7,Fmean as many as 74,000 women are
OL,8,Fforced to leave their job every year.
OL,10,FHalf of pregnant women, those on
OL,11,Fmaternity leave, and those returning
OL,12,Ffrom maternity leave said they had a
OL,13,Fnegative experience at work, leading
OL,14,Fone in five to quit their job,
OL,15,Faccording to the research.
