OL,6,FA third of women said they were
OL,7,Fsidelined or demoted whilst pregnant,
OL,8,Fon maternity leave, or when they
OL,9,Freturn from maternity leave, but only
OL,10,F2% of women who experience
OL,11,Fdiscrimination took a claim to a
OL,12,Ftribunal, said the report.
OL,14,FJoeli Brearley, founder of Pregnant
OL,15,FThen Screwed, said: "We have long
OL,16,Fsuspected things are getting worse,
OL,17,Fnot better. Our free advice line is
OL,18,Fringing off the hook, it has reached a
OL,19,Fpoint where we simply cannot cope with
OL,20,Fdemand.
