OL,6,F"To find that 74,000 mothers a year
OL,7,Fare being pushed out of their job for
OL,8,Fdaring to procreate is not surprising,
OL,9,Fbut it is devastating.
OL,11,F"In 2016, the coalition government
OL,12,Fcommissioned a report to better
OL,13,Funderstand how widespread pregnancy
OL,14,Fand maternity discrimination is.
OL,16,F"The report found that things had
OL,17,Fsignificantly deteriorated over the
OL,18,Fprevious 10 years. Despite committing
OL,19,Fto repeat the research every five
OL,20,Fyears, this has not happened.
