OL,6,FThe campaign groups urged companies to
OL,7,Fincrease their paternity leave offer,
OL,8,Fcreate family friendly workplaces,
OL,9,Fincluding advertising jobs as flexible
OL,10,Fand collect maternity retention data.
OL,12,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,13,F"This is just plain wrong. No one
OL,14,Fshould be losing their job as a result
OL,15,Fof getting pregnant.
OL,17,F"This is why the measures in the
OL,18,FEmployment Rights Bill, such as giving
OL,19,Fpregnant women and new mothers a
OL,20,Fperiod where they are protected from
OL,21,Fbeing dismissed, are so important.
